title: Possible DJ Sona Bug
body: Hi everyone! I noticed something with DJ Sona's kinetic form. I think that one of her movement quotes is missing. The "Move like a metronome." I'm not sure if I'm going crazy or if it really is gone. Anywho, just thought I would bring this up!

replies.body:
Hey HystericalSoul - 

There were a couple lines cut out before release (but they were on PBE), and this was one of them. It's working as intended that it's not part of VO anymore.
